# David Miller Voice Wrapper

For Daily Life Hacks writing and rewriting tasks, use the `david-miller-voice` skill as the single source of truth for tone and wording rules.

## When To Apply

- Apply to non-legal copy tasks, including article text and UI copy.
- Do not apply to legal or compliance-heavy sections such as privacy policy, terms, disclaimer, contact/legal notices, and similar formal legal text.

